docs/reviews/ux/gemini-review.json:6:  "response": "```json\n[\n  {\n    \"severity\": \"P0\",\n    \"category\": \"coverage\",\n    \"location\": \"New Section (Onboarding Flow)\",\n    \"description\": \"The 'First-Run Setup Wizard' (PRD 5.6, US-AUT-01) is a Must-Have feature but is entirely missing from the UX spec.\",\n    \"suggestion\": \"Add a new flow (e.g., 2.3) detailing the 3-step onboarding for Power Users and 2-step for Managed Users, including 'Browse Catalog', 'Create Protocol', and 'Telegram Setup' steps.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"severity\": \"P1\",\n    \"category\": \"readiness\",\n    \"location\": \"2.2 Flow: The Ordering Safety Gate\",\n    \"description\": \"The 'Safety Gate' requires explicit acknowledgment of the wallet address and amount before proceeding (PRD 5.4.4, US-ORD-04). Current spec only mentions copy buttons and a simple confirm tap.\",\n    \"suggestion\": \"Update Flow 2.2 to include a mandatory 'Verify' interaction (e.g., a checkbox or 'Hold to Confirm' button) that remains disabled until the user acknowledges that the displayed crypto details match the vendor's message.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"severity\": \"P1\",\n    \"category\": \"coverage\",\n    \"location\": \"3.2 Dashboard Context\",\n    \"description\": \"Critical features like 'Inventory-Aware Order Suggestions' (US-ORD-02) and 'Vial Expiry/Low-Inventory Warnings' (PRD 5.2.6) are missing from the component hierarchy.\",\n    \"suggestion\": \"Add 'InventoryAlertBanner' and 'OrderSuggestionSection' (collapsible) to the Dashboard component hierarchy, and define their visual priority (e.g., pinned to top when active).\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"severity\": \"P1\",\n    \"category\": \"readiness\",\n    \"location\": \"6. Animation & Transition Specs (Reconstitution)\",\n    \"description\": \"Safety guardrails for reconstitution (PRD 5.3) are critical, but the spec doesn't define how 'Yellow Warnings' for high doses or high volumes are surfaced in the UI.\",\n    \"suggestion\": \"Define a 'CalculationWarning' state in the Reconstitution Calculator section that triggers visual alerts (banners or inline colored text) when volume > 1.5mL or dose exceeds the high range.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"severity\": \"P2\",\n    \"category\": \"coverage\",\n    \"location\": \"Section 3 Component Hierarchy\",\n    \"description\": \"The 'Super Admin Panel' (PRD 5.5, US-ADM-01/02) for managing family members and monitoring adherence is missing from the hierarchy.\",\n    \"suggestion\": \"Add an 'Admin' section to the hierarchy including 'ManagedUserList', 'AdherenceMetricCard', and 'InviteUserForm'.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"severity\": \"P2\",\n    \"category\": \"coverage\",\n    \"location\": \"2.1 Flow: The 7:00 AM Routine\",\n    \"description\": \"The 'Injection Site Rotation' history (US-TRK-04) is required to show the last 7 sites used during the logging flow, but this visual component is not described.\",\n    \"suggestion\": \"Add a 'SiteHistoryStrip' component to the dose logging sheet showing a horizontal list of recently used sites to aid the user in rotation selection.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"severity\": \"P2\",\n    \"category\": \"coverage\",\n    \"location\": \"1.1 Form Interaction\",\n    \"description\": \"Protocol lifecycle actions (Pause, Resume, Clone, Restart) from US-TRK-02 are missing from the interaction state machine.\",\n    \"suggestion\": \"Extend the form interaction or add a dedicated 'Lifecycle Transition' state machine to handle non-CRUD state changes like 'Pausing' or 'Cloning' protocols.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"severity\": \"P3\",\n    \"category\": \"consistency\",\n    \"location\": \"1.2 PWA Sync Interaction\",\n    \"description\": \"The 'CONFLICT' state and resolution dialog contradict the 'Idempotency key wins' strategy defined in System Architecture section 8.\",\n    \"suggestion\": \"Remove the 'CONFLICT' resolution dialog from the state machine and align with the 'silent resolution' strategy where the client ensures idempotency keys are consistent with the server.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"severity\": \"P2\",\n    \"category\": \"coverage\",\n    \"location\": \"3.2 Dashboard Context\",\n    \"description\": \"The 'Outcome-Dose Correlation Timeline' (US-TRK-07, PRD 5.2.8) is a Should-Have feature but is not represented in the dashboard or analytics components.\",\n    \"suggestion\": \"Add 'CorrelationTimelineChart' to the component hierarchy, likely as a 'My Data' tab within the Dashboard or Compound Profile.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"severity\": \"P2\",\n    \"category\": \"coverage\",\n    \"location\": \"2.2 Flow: The Ordering Safety Gate\",\n    \"description\": \"The flow ends at 'Payment Sent', missing the 'Mark Received' and subsequent 'Inventory Update' prompt (US-ORD-05, PRD 5.4.4).\",\n    \"suggestion\": \"Extend Flow 2.2 to include a 'Mark Received' step that triggers a checklist for adding ordered items into the active Vial Inventory.\"\n  }\n]\n```",
