docs/reviews/ux/codex-review.json:3053:    "description": "Reference stories US-REF-01 and US-REF-02 have no components for catalog search, category filters, profile detail, citations, dosing ranges, routes, or stacking notes.",
docs/reviews/ux/codex-review.json:3060:    "description": "Tracker coverage is limited to batch logging; US-TRK-01, US-TRK-02, US-TRK-03 single-dose skip/confirm, US-TRK-04 injection history, US-TRK-08 cycle creation, and US-TRK-09 reminders are not specified.",
docs/reviews/ux/codex-review.json:3067:    "description": "OutcomeEntry is listed, but US-TRK-06 and US-TRK-07 lack UX for 1000-character notes, tag selection, 30/90-day correlation timeline, dual-axis chart, and dosed vs non-dosed stats.",
docs/reviews/ux/codex-review.json:3074:    "description": "Reconstitution stories US-REC-01 and US-REC-02 have no actual flow or component spec for inputs, calculated outputs, warnings, last-dose context, save-vial action, expiry, or inventory decrement behavior.",
docs/reviews/ux/codex-review.json:3081:    "description": "Ordering coverage skips US-ORD-01, US-ORD-02, US-ORD-03, US-ORD-05, US-ORD-06, and most of US-ORD-07: Telegram setup, inventory suggestions, cart, MTProto send/fallback, vendor catalog, receive-to-inventory, stale/cancel states.",
docs/reviews/ux/codex-review.json:3088:    "description": "Multi-user/admin stories US-ADM-01 through US-ADM-03 have no admin panel, invite flow, managed-user simplified dashboard, adherence metric display, deactivation, or password-reset UX.",
docs/reviews/ux/codex-review.json:3095:    "description": "Auth/account stories US-AUT-01 through US-AUT-05 are not covered: registration, login, password reset, onboarding variants, data export, deletion delay, PWA install prompt, and offline shell behavior are absent.",
